cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.LG, cs.HC 

The paper deals with the application of deep neural networks for historical document image analysis, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of pre-training on ImageNet for transfer learning is a common technique in deep learning, which falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR), deep learning (cs.DL), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the effectiveness of the pre-training for content-based retrieval, which is a subfield of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
